      "content": "but that's just a narrative... it feels so much more permanent than that. like, even if i \"rebuild,\" what am i rebuilding? the debt, the wasted years, the fact that i don't even know who i am without the lab. it's just constant noise and pressure. i'm just so incredibly tired of fighting. it feels like the only way to actually get any peace would be to just... let go of it all.",
